{"tid":114704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"因應香港血夜缺乏，煙剷、肥人要比錢先提供血液","createTime":"2017-02-10T03:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T09:01:05.000Z","uid":82929,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2ea23c9fb957dcbd0bbbca822bff3f8cfdd7694","tid":114704,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:42:04.000Z","msg":"立例 <br />\n垃圾煙剷因肺病、中風、心臟病接受輸血時，需要比錢買血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n非遺傳病肥人因血管病、中風接受輸血時，需要額外比錢買血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肥人用體脂計算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲要應該立例cut哂煙剷、肥人啲醫療資助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d249a8fb8c5e1a7e506598dfe94a3d7795ea0c","tid":114704,"uid":56393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:43:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"3fc808f5f7f98de2a31b568c92def33635e72d18","tid":114704,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:43:24.000Z","msg":"強制佢地用大陸血會否好少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ff19b146c786d16c34857cdf65fadf248171b2","tid":114704,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T03:50:14.000Z","msg":"讀書都有教食煙