id":114704,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:08:01.000Z","msg":"煙民買保險都貴啲<br />\n憑咩免費接受無償捐血，立例收返班仆街錢買大陸血就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c677b9945bb6b260bf12c094087104a756a1afa9","tid":114704,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:09:51.000Z","msg":"缺乏--&gt;短缺"},{"pid":"2e7a56c78151cafda8d72c1298b5f52cc215cb25","tid":114704,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁如果呢班人都有份捐血呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食得煙，肝功能好得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n煙剷捐左血都用唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賣返比大陸就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731fba8bf996f953558a75446a58537acf9f52ff","tid":114704,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:14:29.000Z","msg":"諗左好多咩叫血夜 所以決定入po睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d008ca6a6c0f1eae3264c62e9cd8772c6f297eb8","tid":114704,"uid":38540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:14:55.000Z","msg":"其實一早要<br />\n點解要納稅人承擔班煙剷既後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdd35aa0a5b3bea58f22167e830a0165cd48988","tid":114704,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:15:48.000Z","msg":"仲有投建制大中華既廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe23736d1c8fb69c039d4406036ba47dc2197b8","tid":114704,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04: