.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 攞明就搞你先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51688a46169f2f45eafb6b11888e930bc466a966","tid":114704,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:29:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁梁天琦同黃洋達同教主呢？</blockquote><br />\n你數少左長毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有錢咪有中國血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇錢咪死，幾簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2cd29b7a1d749b1e4978428461950ae16f59e1","tid":114704,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁梁天琦同黃洋達同教主呢？</blockquote><br />\n佢地班假本土又邊識做show，為本土血庫着想，搞個戒煙show。<br />\n<br />\n識玩政治就一早選到垃圾會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b2efd1e0cf1c5524e2c6cf0e30313323f4be36","tid":114704,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:46:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔記得瑞典定瑞士，煙鏟無政府醫保，勁正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港都要，cut哂班撚屌啲醫療資助，收返私院價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc777d4fe963024bab13ee7d11e4d7b151f565ff","tid":114704,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5M2fL7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5M2fL7Q.jpg&h=97432259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><